@startuml
title B8 Deep RAG Hardening Plan

skinparam backgroundColor #0B1020
skinparam defaultFontName "Noto Sans CJK KR"
skinparam ArrowColor #86A8FF
skinparam RectangleBorderColor #5B6B8C
skinparam RectangleFontColor #E8ECF8
skinparam RectangleBackgroundColor #131A2B
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #1B2438
skinparam NoteBorderColor #5B6B8C
skinparam NoteFontColor #D7DCEC

rectangle "Slice 1\nGraph-Assisted Retrieval\nCOMPLETED" as S1 #1D4D31
rectangle "Slice 2\nSymbol / Dependency Graph\nNEXT" as S2 #5A4520
rectangle "Slice 3\nVersion-Aware Retrieval" as S3 #2B3348
rectangle "Slice 4\nCache + Incremental Reindex" as S4 #2B3348
rectangle "Slice 5\nRole-Specific Personalization" as S5 #2B3348

rectangle "relevance" as R #17304A
rectangle "temporal validity" as T #17304A
rectangle "cost / latency" as C #17304A
rectangle "adaptation" as A #17304A

S1 --> S2
S2 --> S3
S3 --> S4
S4 --> S5

S2 --> R
S3 --> T
S4 --> C
S5 --> A

note right of S2
code_symbols
code_symbol_edges
TS / Go / Python first
1-hop traversal
end note

note right of S3
knowledge_document_versions
branch / commit affinity
stale branch penalty
end note

note right of S4
retrieval cache entries
project knowledge revision
incremental import
end note

note right of S5
retrieval feedback events
role profiles
explainable boosts only
end note

@enduml
